{"tid":738305,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"無賴男打尖唔認錯　車長神回獲激讚","createTime":"2018-07-11T12:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T12:58:36.000Z","uid":19552,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c90e42bf8d8c76162d05e0891b6bc44ac4a74a4b","tid":738305,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:10:27.000Z","msg":"搭巴士守秩序登車是常識，可惜總有人會挑戰一些規矩。昨日（10日）傍晚就有一名男乘客登車時打尖，被巴士車長出言指摘。豈料男子毫無悔意，反嘲車長「成世揸巴士」。車長一句「神回」，惹來一眾網民激讚。<br />\n<br />\n現場是紅磡海底隧道收費廣場巴士站，一輛往香港方向的巴士在隧道口上客，一名身穿紫色外衣的中年男子率先登車，惟車長發現對方打尖，提醒對方排隊：「你見唔到後面有條（人）龍㗎？」 <br />\n<br />\n已走進車廂的男乘客聞言，回頭走到車長旁，態度囂張地說：「咁依家見到，咁點丫？」車長要求對方落車，讓其他人先登車，惟男乘客竟堅稱：「睇唔到（人龍），我係睇唔到，唔係打尖。」車長立即踢爆，表明目擊他由欄杆「擒出」，不可能看不到。<br />\n<br />\n男乘客其後表現得更加晦氣，「我畀人上晒揀晒位最後至上！」最後更謂：「你滿意未，巴士佬，成世揸巴士啦你！」車長聞言，極快回應：「咁你成世搭巴士啦...我成世揸冇問題，有人工出，你咪成世搭巴士囉！」 <br />\n<br />\n車長的「神級回應」惹來一眾網民激讚，指「車長講得非常好」、「司機維持秩序好正常，支持」，有網民更質疑該乘客「明明自己錯都要死撐落去」、「扮傻打尖仲好意思大聲夾惡，做人點解可以咁無賴？」"},{"pid":"659f604a48c5e573ba088e77c7b474627c8618d4","tid":738305,"uid":42275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:11:25.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑"},{"pid":"41c4d887802c6c1c0d12c0f22e614b9bd3b334e9","tid":738305,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fba1c531765102c903401ae2273c8d424d847fe9","tid":738305,"uid":78016,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"宜家的稿費真好賺"},{"pid":"65cb4357274576c70639fe0adb0cb21e40db29dc","tid":738305,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:13:56.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/mobile/bkn-20180711172734096-0711_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180711%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180711172734096-0711_00822_001.html&d=0RoAtFcd%2FKvjBHT0hgqWWMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=ae29027f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180711/mobile/bkn-20180711172734096-0711_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1a78afac5ca8dc73d9a8725eb1039b92158daca3","tid":738305,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 柒頭皮又要搭又要屌<br />\n想型既就落車唔搭先屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c827a60f805000b10b9795c88cc87da952d45932","tid":738305,"uid":151664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a0a176d39d0a1006a754690455ab6a4f1ab39a","tid":738305,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac16148d38b1c72a1e112ab31d5eb2a8d09052d5","tid":738305,"uid":40061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:56:19.000Z","msg":"件中坑咁快唔記得馬場巴士攬炒單野<br />\n仲敢聊啲巴士佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53d3d2c515a0291b00394999aa76d8c5401e08d","tid":738305,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T12:58:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}